==經濟==
[[File:Pumpjacks.JPG|thumb]]

克恩县以農業作為經濟支柱之一，並且是一個重要的[[石油|石油]]及[[天然气|天然气]]生產地。克恩县佔了整個美國石油產量的十分之一，且克恩县在美國五大油田中已佔有三個。還因其礦產而聞名，其礦產包括[[黃金|黃金]]、[[硼酸鹽|硼酸鹽]]和[[四水硼砂|四水硼砂]]。加利福尼亞州最大的露天礦場亦位於克恩县內。<ref name="Rio Tinto Borax home page">{{cite web |url=http://www.borax.com/index.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-07-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070630064418/http://www.borax.com/index.html |archivedate=2007-06-30 }} Rio Tinto Borax. Accessed July 3, 2007.</ref>

截至2009年，克恩县在加州52,144個油井中佔了81%。<ref Name="2008rpt">{{cite web  | last =   | first =   | authorlink =   | coauthors =   | title = 2008 Report of the state oil & gas supervisor  | work = Department of Oil, Gas, and Geothermal Resources  | publisher = California Department of Conservation ("DOGGR 2009")  | year = 2009  | url = ftp://ftp.consrv.ca.gov/pub/oil/annual_reports/2008/PR06_Annual_2008.pdf  | format =   | doi =   | accessdate = March 10, 2010  | archive-date = 2017-05-25  | archive-url = https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20170525054948/ftp://ftp.consrv.ca.gov/pub/oil/annual_reports/2008/PR06_Annual_2008.pdf  | dead-url = yes  }} p. 66</ref>而加州超過四分之三的石油產量均來自克恩县。<ref name="Conservation p. 2">[ftp://ftp.consrv.ca.gov/pub/oil/annual_reports/2006/0102stats_06.pdf California Department of Conservation, Oil and Gas Statistics, Annual Report, December 31, 2006] {{Webarchive|url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20170525054318/ftp://ftp.consrv.ca.gov/pub/oil/annual_reports/2006/0102stats_06.pdf |date=2017-05-25 }}, p. 2</ref>

